text: Kemily Leão (born 22 March 2000) is a Brazilian water polo player. She was part of the Brazilian women's water polo team at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * leao-kemily wrsd.lima2019 * beograd2018 * fina-funchal2019 Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian water polo players
